	<article class="post-614948 post type-post status-publish hentry category-industrials category-mergers-acquisitions tag-alstom tag-general-electric-company tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-mitsubishi-heavy-industries-limited tag-siemens-ag des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures org-alstom org-general-electric-company org-mitsubishi-heavy-industries-limited org-siemens-ag" id="post-614948">
